data.Name: Parker Millsap
data.Bio: Parker Millsap is an American singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist from Purcell, Oklahoma playing a blend of blues, country, alt-country/Americana, and folk music. Influenced by his Pentecostal Church and the Blues Radio Times, with his parents Millsap created a sound between country, alt-country, folk, traditional. americana, blues and rock. While Millsap plays harp, acoustic- and slideguitar, you also find acoustic-bass and violin in his band. Read more on Last.fm
